GameLogic - Class in fi.tuni.tiko
Class for handling changes of game state and ingame resources Dispatcher of events to classes that need to listen to that All elements that need to listen to game state or resource changes should subscribe to gameLogicListeners list
GameLogic() - Constructor for class fi.tuni.tiko.GameLogic
 
GameLogic.GameState - Enum in fi.tuni.tiko
Enum to trigger correct events based on what state the game is currently in for instance clicking the play button in main menu will change change the game state to MAP_SELECTION and will trigger all the events needed for the settings screen
GameLogic.Language - Enum in fi.tuni.tiko
Enum for triggering correct events based on language setting
GameLogicListener - Interface in fi.tuni.tiko
Listener for events about game state and resource changes All classes that need information about game state or resource changes should implement this
GameObject - Interface in fi.tuni.tiko.gameObject
All objects on the maps should implement this Or extend a class that implements this
GameObject.TYPE - Enum in fi.tuni.tiko.gameObject
 
GameObjectManager - Class in fi.tuni.tiko.gameObject
